                      <h3 class="u-text u-text-2">OUR CEO</h3>
                      <p class="u-text u-text-3">Nana Banyin Ayeyi Djan is a third year computer science student at Ashesi University in the class of 2023. He is 20 yearls of and aspires to be a website developer in the future. He has many side interests like graphic design and video editing. His hobbies include Basketball, Graphic design, video editing and Drumming. The reason he took on this project is because during the Covid-19 pandemic, when chores were being allocated in his home, there was always an argument about who should do which chore, who spoilt which equipment and other arguments. He pondered over ways to stop this argument and he came up with ChoresUp.</p>
